{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_03_01",
  "title": "鈴村優 1話 ライブの後は…？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_lesson_noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――クリスマスイブ前日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—The day before Christmas Eve",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1500,
          "startTime": 1.5
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1700,
          "startTime": 1.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、急で悪いんだけど\nライブの衣装で相談が――あれ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry for springing this on you‚\nbut we need to discuss costumes for the concert—Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3381.6778977000004,
          "startTime": 7.9816778977
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、{user}さん、こんにちは～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello there‚ {user}!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.7150112311,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんとすみれちゃんなら、今外出してますわ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you’re looking for Rui and Sumire‚ they’re out now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.657528305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そうや\nぶぶ漬けでも食べながらお待ちになります？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚\nhow about we eat some bubuzuke or something while we wait?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ぶぶ漬けって……え？　……え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Bubuzuke? What?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "確か京都の人がお客を追い返す時の常套句だったよな？\n……鈴村さん、もしかして怒ってる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wasn’t that a standard expression Kyoto people use for getting rid of guests?\nSuzumura… are you angry with me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "いややわぁ、冗談やんか\n今時そんなこと言いませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nahh‚ just kidding.\nPeople don’t say that these days.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "それに、ちぃーとも怒ってなんていませんよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And‚ I’m not even the teensiest bit angry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスライブなんて、素敵なお仕事取ってくれた\n{user}さんには、ほんま感謝してます～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You got us the Christmas concert‚ which is a great opportunity‚\nso I’m really grateful to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだよな？　ははは、それなら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? Hahaha. In that case…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "そうですよ～。ライブの後は取材まで入ってるし\nほんま、ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s true. And we even get to meet the reporters after the show‚\nso really‚ thank you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "おかげさまで\nうちらの予定、ぽーんと吹っ飛んでしまいましたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And thanks to all that‚\nall our plans just got called off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "ライブの後、うちら三人でクリスマスパーティーやるん\nめっちゃ楽しみにしてたんですけどね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After the show‚ the three of us were going to have a Christmas party.\nWe were so looking forward to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "うっ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oof…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.5666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_heart-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 78.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "実はすみれちゃん、うちと瑠依ちゃんに内緒で\nサプライズパーティーを準備しとったみたいで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire seems to have been preparing a surprise party for us‚\nwithout telling Rui and me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "うちと瑠依ちゃん、気づかん振りして\nこっそりすみれちゃんのこと、見守ってたんやけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui and I were pretending not to know.\nWe’ve been quietly watching over Sumire‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "それが空振って……へこんでしまって……\nそれも仕方ないなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and now that’s not happening‚ she’s feeling down…\nThat can’t be helped either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ううっ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ack…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_heart-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 99.1
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_heart-01.m4a",
          "delay": 100.00000000000853,
          "startTime": 99.2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "あ～あ、こんな仕事熱心なマネージャーさんが\nうちらの担当で、幸せですわぁ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh* I’m glad we have such an enthusiastic\nmanager to handle us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "す、すまない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "いややわ～。謝らんとって\nうち、ちっとも根に持ってへんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ please don’t apologize.\nI don’t resent it at all‚ not in the least.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "持ってるだろ？　絶対、根に持ってるよな？\nいっそ、はっきりそう言ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You do. You totally resent me‚ don’t you?\nSo please just say so.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "何言うてんの、うちがそんなまさか～\n……あ、ぶぶ漬け用意しますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you on about? I don’t feel that way at all.\nAh‚ I’ll get the bubuzuke ready.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……鈴村さん、レッスンが終わったら\nこの件について話がしたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzumura‚ once the lesson’s over‚\nI want to talk about this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "あら、なんか気を遣わせて申し訳ないです～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ I’m sorry for troubling you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 140.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "トリエル三人でクリスマスパーティーをするのは\n初めてだったのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Was this the first time you three were\ngoing to have a Christmas party?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "せやで、バンプロ時代の年末年始は\n分刻みで、スケジュールびっしりやったしなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. When we were at Van Productions‚ our schedule\naround New Year was packed to the last minute.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "姫野さん、仕事の鬼やったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ms. Himeno was a workhorse‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "あの頃、うちらはまだまだ新人やし\nもちろんありがたかってんけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and back then we were still just newcomers‚\nso we were grateful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "人気アイドルは年末年始のイベントに\n引っ張りだこだからな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone wants the popular idols\nfor year-end events…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu020.m4a",
      "text": "せやから、今回はうちら、めっちゃ喜んでたんやわ\n初めて全員オフやっ！　て",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So this year‚ we were really happy.\nAll of us with time off‚ for the first time ever!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "それで奥山さんがパーティーを計画してたのに\n俺が仕事を入れてしまった、と",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And Okuyama was planning a party‚\nbut then I scheduled a job…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu021.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、まぁ、経営者目線？　では\n仕方ないかもですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. Well‚ maybe from the management perspective\nit can’t be helped…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu022.m4a",
      "text": "でもな～……連絡きたの昨日やし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ we only heard yesterday‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu023.m4a",
      "text": "うち、あのメッセ見た時、思ったわ\n……ここにも仕事の鬼がおるって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and when I saw the message‚ I thought‚\n“Looks like we have a workhorse here too.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu024.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "分かった、悪かったよ……\n俺に出来ることならなんでもする！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ it’s my bad.\nI’ll do whatever I can to make up for it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 203.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu025.m4a",
      "text": "……えっ？　ほんまに～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Seriously?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu026.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ……ライブの後の取材だけ\n別日にずらしてもらうのって……可能ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ would it be possible to move just the\npress conference after the show to another day?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 212.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな……それならなんとか出来そうだ\n任せてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let me see… I could probably do something about that.\nLeave it to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu027.m4a",
      "text": "お詫びにはならんかもしれへんけど……\n取材は、いつもよりサービス多めで頑張りますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It might not do as an apology‚\nbut we’ll do our best with extra service for the press.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 224.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、鈴村さんがそうしてくれるなら\n相手方も気持ち良く相談に乗ってくれそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ if you could do that‚ Suzumura‚\nit’ll be easier for them to accept it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 231.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスライブ後と、その次の日も\nトリエルは全員オフにする。三人で楽しんでくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The two days after the Christmas concert are\nday offs for all three of you‚ so you should enjoy it together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 236.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-yu028.m4a",
      "text": "さすが{user}さんは\nマネージャーの鑑や。鬼やなくて仏やわ～なむなむ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks‚ {user}.\nAs ever‚ you’re the model of a manager. You’re an angel‚ not a workhorse.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_03_01-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "拝むのはやめてくれないか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ you can knock off worshipping me now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 248.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}